# Architecture

**Template scope:** Better Auth (`auth`) schema only in core — no product-specific Prisma domains in shared dashboard `lib/`. Features are removable subtrees (CLI-ready).

**Dependency:** sub-feature → segment `lib/` → `src/lib` | `src/components`. No cross-sibling imports (e.g. `members/` → not `teams/`).

**Colocate:** pages, UI, feature `lib/`, actions at `src/app/action/<feature>/` (one mutation per file).

**Single source of truth:** `*-routes.ts` and `cache-tags.ts` per segment; badges in shared config; UI from `src/components/ui` (shadcn defaults). Base UI links: `render={<Link … />}`, not `asChild`.

Before new helpers: pick scope upward; compose shadcn primitives first; stay minimal.

**UI:** [ui-design.md](docs/agents/ui-design.md).

